[[File:Shandeir, others.png|thumb|right|250px|Shandeir and her traveling companions ''en route'' to [[Elturel]].]]
Some time before the {{YearlinkName|1492}},<ref group="note">These events take place during or before [[1492 DR]], when the truth about [[the Companion]] was revealed. Shandeir traveled aboard the ''[[Hesperornis]]'' back to [[Elturel]], along with her companions [[Falaster Fisk]], Great Reader [[Sylvira Savikas]], and [[Jaskir Dawn]]. She was enlisted to help decipher the text of the ''Tome of Zariel'' to aid High Overseer [[Thavius Kreeg]]. Aboard the ship Shandeir met and took a liking to the spirited young wizard [[Helene]].{{Cite comic/A Darkened Wish 2|9-11}}

The ship met an unfortunate fate when it landed at [[Mintarn]], just before the isle and its docks were attacked by the [[red dragon]] [[Hoondarrh]].{{Cite comic/A Darkened Wish 2|12-14}}{{Cite comic/A Darkened Wish 3|6-7}} Her tome was recovered be Helene, who used it to communicate with a mysterious being and bargain for greater power.
